Class TranslationValue

java.lang.Object
de.dei0.blockprot.bukkit.TranslationValue
public final class TranslationValue extends Object
Represents the default string value and a translated value of it, as loaded through Translator.loadFromConfigs(YamlConfiguration, YamlConfiguration).
Since:
0.4.6

    • getValue

      @NotNull public @NotNull String getValue()

      Returns:
